def bubble_sort(arr):

    for i in range(n):

        for j in range(0, n - i - 1):
            # Swap if the element found is greater than the next element
            if arr[j] > arr[j + 1]:
                arr[j], arr[j + 1] = arr[j + 1], arr[j]
                swapped = True
        
        # If no swapping occurred, array is already sorted
        if not swapped:
            break
    return arr
